    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Knife Collectors Rejoice! Now introducing the special edition etched dagger set: Wolf, Eagle, and Dragon Daggers with their respective sheaths. This is a beautifully crafted dagger set featuring 3 different outdoor graphic scenes etched onto the Scabbard and handle. The handles' pommels are made with impressive animal heads of the distinctive graphic depicted throughout the handle.<br><br>Each ASR Outdoor Fixed Blade Animal Dagger has a handle in the shape of it's respective animal and the blade is acid etched with a impressively detailed design. Both the handle and sheath feature a colorful and majestic design depicting the spirit of the animal. The blade of these daggers are 8 inches length and is made from strong 440 Stainless Steel. The total knife length is 13.75\" from point to pommel</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n\n  \n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t