ight{float:right !important;}\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t</style>\n\n  \n  \n\t  <!-- Static navbar -->\n\t      <div class=\"navbar navbar-default\" role=\"navigation\">\n\t        <div class=\"container\">\n\t          <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n\t            <!-- ADD YOUR SELLER NAME OR LOGO HERE -->\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/irongateamericansupply\">Irongate American Supply</a>\n\t          </div>\n\t          <div class=\"navbar-collapse collapse\">\n\t            <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n\t\t      <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n\t              <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/irongateamericansupply\">Our eBay Store</a></li>\n\t              <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/irongateamericansupply?_trksid=p2047675.l2559\">About Us</a></li>\n\t              <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/contact/sendmsg?&amp;recipient=irongateamericansupply\">Contact Us</a></li>\n\t            </ul>\n\t          </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n\t        </div>\n\t      </div>\n\n\n\t      <div class=\"container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"main-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/hobby_knives/H-4852-XX_animal_dagger_parent_01.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t          <h1>3pc Animal Head Fixed Blade Ornamental Dagger Collector Knife Decorative Gift Set, Wolf Eagle and Dragon</h1>\n\t\t\t  <h2>MSRP 69.99</h2>\n\t\t\t  <h3>ASR Outdoor</h3>\n\t          <p data-start=\"276\" data-end=\"618\">Step into a world of fantasy and medieval design with this <strong data-start=\"335\" data-end=\"368\">3-piece decorative dagger set</strong>, featuring bold <strong data-start=\"385\" data-end=\"427\">Dragon, Wolf, and Eagle themed daggers</strong>. Designed for collectors and fans of fantasy-inspired décor, this set combines detailed craftsmanship with striking visual appeal, making it a standout addition to any collection or display.</p>\n<p data-start=\"620\" data-end=\"909\">Each dagger showcases an <strong data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"674\">ornate animal head handle</strong>, paired with a <strong data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"718\">matching themed scabbard</strong> and a <strong data-start=\"725\" data-end=\"764\">finely etched stainless steel blade</strong>. The detailed artwork and engraved designs give each piece a unique identity while maintaining a cohesive fantasy aesthetic across the full set.</p>\n<p data-start=\"911\" data-end=\"1218\">Crafted with <strong data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"954\">440 stainless steel blades</strong>, these daggers offer durability while maintaining their primary purpose as <strong data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1070\">display pieces and collectible items</strong>. The combination of etched blades, sculpted handles, and vibrant scabbard artwork creates a premium look ideal for shelves, cases, or themed rooms.</p><p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1536\">This <strong data-start=\"1225\" data-end=\"1247\">fantasy dagger set</strong> is perfect for a wide range of enthusiasts, including <strong data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1380\">DnD players, cosplay fans, medieval décor collectors, and knife collectors</strong>. Whether you're building a display, enhancing a costume setup, or searching for a unique gift, this set delivers strong visual impact and collector appeal.</p><p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1536\">These knives are truly unique and are sure to amaze and delight anyone who sets their eyes on it. This set is a must-have for any knife lover, and will display prominently anywhere that it is placed; this set truly makes for a great gift for the knife collector who has it all or is just beginning to collect</p>\n\n\n\t\t\t  <h3>Product Details</h3>\n\t\t\t  <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR 